title: Week 8 preview & Dolphins vs. Patriots recap
itunes:title: Week 8 preview & Dolphins vs. Patriots recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler - welcome in NFL Media's Andrew Siciliano as they break down each Week 8 matchup. Plus, the heroes recap the Patriots 36-7 victory over the Dolphins as New England improves to a perfect 7-0 record.
